{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 36,
  "title": "第三十六章（微明）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "將欲翕之 必固張之 將欲弱之 必固強之 將欲去之 必固與之 將欲奪之 必固予之 是謂微明"
    },
    {
      "text": "柔弱勝強"
    },
    {
      "text": "魚不可脫於淵 邦利器不可以示人"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先開張之者，欲極其奢淫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先強大之者，欲使遇禍患。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先興之者，欲使其驕危。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先與之者，欲極其貪心。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 40,
          "end": 41
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此四事，其道微，其效明也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "柔弱者久長，剛強者先亡也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "魚脫於淵，謂去剛得柔，不可複製焉。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "利器者，謂權道也。治國權者，不可以示執事之臣也。治身道者，不可以示非其人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "將欲除强梁，去暴亂，當以此四者。因物之性，令其自戮，不假刑為大，以除將物也，故曰微明也。足其張，令之足，而又求其張，則眾所歙也，與其張之不足，而改其求張者，愈益而已反危。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "利器，利國之器也。唯因物之性，不假刑以理物，器不可覩，而物各得其所，則國之利器也。示人者，任刑也。刑以利國則失矣。魚脫於淵，則必見失矣。利國器而立刑以示人，亦必失也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
